  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes the Hawaii Micro-Lending Credit Enhancement Program within the Department of Business, Economic Development, and Tourism to expand micro-lending capacity by providing state\u2011funded loan loss reserves or other credit enhancement that absorbs first losses on qualified micro-loans made by participating lenders to Hawaii small businesses.  Allows borrower fees and state matching contributions to capitalize lender-held loan loss reserve accounts.  Establishes the Hawaii Micro-Lending Credit Enhancement Special Fund.  Requires reports to the Legislature.  Appropriates funds."
    }
  ],
